sc0 ls0 ws0">杰出的学者之一。<span class="_ _a"></span>他在佛法学修领域，<span class="_ _a"></span>有着卓尔不凡的影响</div><div class="t m0 x9 hc y11c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">力。<span class="_ _8"></span>堪布不仅把藏文经论译成中文，<span class="_ _8"></span>还为论典广作注疏，<span class="_ _8"></span>如</div><div class="t m0 x9 hc y11d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">寂天菩萨的<span class="_ _6"></span>《入行论》<span class="_ _6"></span>等等。<span class="_ _8"></span>参加<span class="_ _6"></span>《佛教基础知识》<span class="_ _6"></span>这门课</div><div class="t m0 x9 hc y11e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">的同学，<span class="_ _a"></span>以后会读到这本书，<span class="_ _a"></span>你们将从中感知到堪布对这部</div><div class="t m0 x9 hc y11f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">论典的无比精通与甚深感悟。 </div><div class="t m0 x1c hc y120 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">堪布不仅对<span class="_ _8"></span>《入行论》<span class="_ _8"></span>做了非常广博的讲解，<span class="_ _6"></span>更围绕传</div><div class="t m0 x9 hc y121 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">统佛教主题，<span class="_ _8"></span>作了大量著述。<span class="_ _8"></span>学过藏传佛教课的同学，<span class="_ _8"></span>已经</div><div class="t m0 x9 hc y122 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">学习过喇荣五明佛学院的历史，<span class="_ _d"></span>熟知堪布的上师晋美彭措法</div><div class="t m0 x9 hc y123 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">王，<span class="_ _a"></span>知道佛学院是真正建立在行为清净的理念之上，<span class="_ _a"></span>并如实</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
